    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">This courseincludes the definition of nutrition and importance of food groups, macro nutrients, micro nutrients, water and drinks, the importance of nutrition in the Prevention of diseases, obesity, popular diets, eating disorders, diseases, nutrition, physical activity, and nutrition covers.</Data></Cell>
