    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Volunteering practices in sports and the importance of volunteering in sports organizations, career management, job description, selection and motivation of volunteers.</Data></Cell>
