   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="45">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 158</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Science Reporting and Popular Science Publishing</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The course includes theoretical and practical studies necessary to develop the skills of both associate and undergraduate students to read, research and write about scientific topics; to train future science reporters and to increase the scientific culture in our country.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411993&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="135">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 162</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Career Planning</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">27.02.2026</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Career planning is, of course, in the framework of the draft created by the Office of the presidential human resources, videos and activities for each week prepared with academics, industry professionals, civil society organizations and international organizations to be invited by a guest, it is suggested that Trainers be processed. Supporting activities to be included in the course are designed to inform students about the methods and tools used in professional applications and to gain the ability to use them in the most effective way and are supported by practical activities. Career centers will follow the course in practice with activities that provide experience opportunities to support students to develop their skills. The proposed program on the structure and content of the course is presented below. The program in question may vary according to the characteristics of universities and departments where students who will take the course are registered.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411997&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="60">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 163</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Technology Addiction</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Within the scope of this course, human interaction with information technologies will be discussed with a developmental perspective. At the end of the course, it is aimed that the students have a theoretical knowledge to discuss the positive and negative aspects of information technology that affect human development, and to define the concept of technology addiction.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412031&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="90">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 166</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Volunteering Studies</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The Concept of Volunteering and Volunteer Management; Basic Volunteering Fields (Disaster and Emergency, Environment, Education and Culture, Sports, Health and Social Services etc.); Project Development Related to Volunteer Work and Participation in Volunteer Work in the Field; Ethics, Moral, Religious, Traditional Values ??and Principles in Voluntary Work; Participation in Voluntary Work in Public Institutions, Local Authorities and Non-Governmental Organizations (NGO); Risk Groups and Volunteering in Society; Immigrants and Volunteering.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412049&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="135">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 167</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Entrepreneurship</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">This course; Testing the entrepreneurship feature, How to find a business idea? Concept of responsible entrepreneurship and sharing of experience with business idea development and creativity exercises. Concept of responsible entrepreneurship and sharing of experience with business idea development and creativity exercises. Workshops on the business model. Canvas business model application studies Creating customer personas and customer maps. Problem solving methods. Business concept, business functions, types, forms of establishment, financial and legal responsibilities. Business Plan Concept and Elements: Market research, Marketing plan, Production plan, management plan, Financial plan How to prepare a business plan, Workshops on the business plan, Evaluation of Entrepreneurship Course and Brainstorming includes topics.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412050&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="45">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 168</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Disability and Life</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The concept of disability, classification of disability and different types of disability, disability rights and social policies, environmental regulations for disability-free life, practices to increase the social integration of the disabled,</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412051&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 169</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Activity</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">What is physical activity? How should physical activity characteristics be in different age groups and diseases? What are the possible solutions to improve the level of physical activity in the society?</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412052&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 170</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Stress Management and Well-Being</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412060&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="60">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 171</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Neuroscience</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The definition of the concept of neuroscience, application areas and basic research methods will be explained. Neurophysiological mechanisms from neuron cell and neural transmission will be summarized. The anatomical structure of the nervous system and the functioning of the human brain will be explained. The most up-to-date research methods in neuroscience are also included in the curriculum.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412058&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="120">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 172</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Communication Skills and Presentation Techniques</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Technical trainings will be given for the use of correct intonation, diction, voice-breathing for correct and effective speech. Theoretical and practical studies will be conducted on the use of body language, posture, color, gesture -facial expressions, which are one of the silent communication elements that have a major role in communication in the course. The field in which the presentation is made ( political, legal, scientific...) according to this, workshops prepared by the students themselves will be held, focusing on the form and style of the speech. During the process, students will watch each other and create a discussion environment. Listening, speaking and staying in the “moment”, which are the basic elements of communication, will be practiced.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412057&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="105">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 173</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Law</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Health Rights Medical Ethics Legal Regulations Legal-Ethical Relations Health Law Patient Rights Illuminated Consent Refusal of Treatment Keeping Secrets Medical Records Choosing a Physician Possession of a Companion Organ and Tissue Transplantation Artificial Insemination Embryo Transplantation Sterilization Surrogate Motherhood Physician Rights and Ethical Responsibility Legal Responsibility of the Physician The obligation to determine the disease(diagnosis-diagnosis) The obligation to choose and apply the method of treatment Obligation to inform the hospital and relatives and to obtain their consent Obligation not to deceive and mislead Obligation to keep secrets Obligation to keep records Obligation to exercise high care</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412059&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="120">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 174</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Environmental Pollution and Climate Change</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Technical trainings will be given for the use of correct intonation, diction, voice-breathing for correct and effective speech. Theoretical and practical studies will be conducted on the use of body language, posture, color, gesture -facial expressions, which are one of the silent communication elements that have a major role in communication in the course. The field in which the presentation is made ( political, legal, scientific...) according to this, workshops prepared by the students themselves will be held, focusing on the form and style of the speech. During the process, students will watch each other and create a discussion environment. Listening, speaking and staying in the “moment”, which are the basic elements of communication, will be practiced.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412056&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
