    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Sound-Breath, Diction Rules, Elements of effective communication, vowel and consonant letters, articulation, differences between written language and spoken language, intonation, emphasis, pause, body language, improvisation.</Data></Cell>
