   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="60">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 215</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Rights and Health</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Basic concepts of human rights; historical development of human rights; the Universal Declaration of human rights, human rights and related regulations at the national and international levels; the different groups of society and different environments in terms of the situation of human rights, human rights, development and social relations of inequality; health as a human right.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412055&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="75">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 217</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">In class, film viewing will consist primarily of clips, shorts, and portions of documentaries about the history of film. In addition, up to fourteen out-of-class viewings may be assigned as required. All viewings should be approached as PRIMARY TEXTS, not just entertainment. You will be required to think &#45;- seriously and critically &#45;- about what you are seeing. That is, an active (rather than passive) viewing is required. The exams will cover the screenings, the lectures and discussions, and the readings.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412030&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="45">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The course will include various guides to understand the genre as a set of narrative conventions, an industrial category, and an affective relationship to the screen. Students can expect to examine a variety of cinematic texts from a mix of critical lenses.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412061&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 223</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Modern Scientific Research Methods</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Scientific research methods, quantitative and qualitative study examples, data analysis through a statistical program, research results, publication and writing techniques, and reporting.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411824&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="60">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 225</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Strategic Brand Management</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Course Content In this course, students will be informed about the key concepts of brand and marketing management. Marketing is a structured process, henceforth, the course will teach how to formulate strategies to engage new and current customers as well as generate sales. Students who attend this course are expected to improve their commercial focus and acquire skills to influence business growth.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411943&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 226</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Project Management</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Principles and methods of international project management</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411942&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="60">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 227</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Sustainability</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Participants of this course will develop a discerning comprehension of the interconnections among ecological, economic, and social systems. They will explore the correlation between urgent environmental challenges and prevalent patterns of production and consumption, while also acquiring knowledge of diverse social sciences methodologies and concepts to scrutinize this phenomenon.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411944&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="120">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 229</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Translational Cancer Research</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Dersin İçeriği Translational cancer research is a critical field that focuses on bridging the gap between basic research discoveries and their practical application in clinical settings. The aim of the course you described is to equip BSc (Bachelor of Science) students with a comprehensive understanding of the tools and techniques used in translational cancer research. Here's a breakdown of what this could entail: Translational cancer research is a critical field that focuses on bridging the gap between basic research discoveries and their practical application in clinical settings. The aim of the course you described is to equip BSc (Bachelor of Science) students with a comprehensive understanding of the tools and techniques used in translational cancer research. Here's a breakdown of what this could entail:</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411945&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 230</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Good Manufacturing Practices (GMP) - Good Laboratory Practices (GLP)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Quality Assurance and Good Manufacturing Practices in Pharmaceutical Manufacturing</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411947&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 231</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Prized Topics in Molecular Biology and Genetics</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The work of Nobel laureates in Physiology or Medicine and Chemistry will be discussed under the headings Genetics, Gene Regulation, Basic Research, Genome Regulation, Translational Research and Immunity.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411847&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="75">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 232</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Social Roles and Identities</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Throughout the lessons, various gender approaches in the literature will be discussed from different perspectives, and in the following processes, students will be asked to choose a material that will enable them to examine the gender roles they encounter in the media in their daily lives. For example, they will be expected to discuss an outdoor visual about breast cancer awareness, which will address the issue of femininity, or prostate cancer awareness, which will address the issue of masculinity.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411848&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 233</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Scientific and Experimental Approach to Vermicomposting</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411849&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="45">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 234</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Media and Health Discourses</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Throughout the lessons, these stereotypes of health discourses will be discussed from different perspectives. In the following lessons, students will be asked to choose a text or material to discuss these stereotypes of health discourses.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411850&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 235</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Stres Management in Health Care</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Stress Management in healthcare and prevention and treatment</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411851&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 236</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Modernisation in Turkey</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412066&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="75">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 237</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Cultural Artifacts and Social Identity</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">This course introduces students the various aspects of evaluating cultural artifacts. The course begins with the theoretical background of culture and its relevant vocabulary. The following path covers an array of topics including, but not limited to, economy, political appearance of culture, media, heritage, and myth. The focus on these topics will be accompanied by structural issues such as inequality, social class, and cultural capital.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412065&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="90">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 238</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Reading and Walking Istanbul</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The objective of this course is to examine the transformation of the City of Istanbul starting from the Turkish Modernity and trace the urban and social developments during the Istanbul’s gaining a global facet. The course will cover different phases and appearances of the urban history and structure of Istanbul. Right to the City, The Understanding of Locality, Urban Gender Relations, Migration, Development of Infrastructure, Formal and Informal Labor Practices, Public Space and Public Health will be part of the readings and discussions.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412064&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 240</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History, Culture and Society of Turkey through Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412089&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="90">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 241</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Microbiota in Health and Disease</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bu ders ile temel kavramlardan başlanılarak tedavi uygulamalarına kadar geniş bir bakış açısıyla mikrobiyomun sağlık ve hastalıktaki rolleri farklı disiplinlerden öğrencilere anlatılacaktır. Bu dersin içeriğinde; Mikrobiyomun tanımı, Mikrobiyomun insan vücudunda gelişimi ve dağılımı, Mikrobiyomun insan sağlığı, metabolizması ve hastalıkları ile ilişkisi, Mikrobiyom-ilaç etkileşimleri, Probiyotik ve prebiyotiklerin farmasötik tedavilerdeki yeri ve fekal mikrobiyota transplantasyonu, Mikrobiyomun toplumsal sağlık üzerindeki etkisi, enfeksiyon kontrolü ve antibiyotik direnci yer almaktadır.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412075&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
   </Row>
