    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">In this course project budgeting , team building , time management , CPM and PERT planning , resource allocation, time and cost analysis , monitoring / control and information systems are taught .</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411827&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
