    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">MBG 015</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">DNA Repair and Mutgenesis</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">24.06.2025</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">In this course, mutagenic agents, DNA damages and structural damages, DNA damage repair pathways, nucleus and mitochondrial DNA damage repair mechanisms, genetic instabilities, mutations and hereditary diseases caused by DNA damage repair mechanisms malfunctioning subjects will be discussed in detail. Moreover, roles of those systems in diagnosis, etiology and pathology of diseases caused by DNA repair mechanisms and DNA repair errors will be examined.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412018&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
