    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Ethics, Resources and Approaches, The Advent of the Golden Era of Animal Alternatives, Models for disease-oriented topics, including cardiac and pulmonary diseases, aging, infectious diseases, obesity, diabetes, neurological diseases, joint diseases, visual disorders, cancer, hypertension, genetic diseases, and diseases of abuse.</Data></Cell>
