    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Learning different properties of matter at different phases; Listing and interpreting chemical variations of liquids, solids and gases.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411921&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
