    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be provided with the knowledge and skills to communicate effectively in family, school, cultural life and business life by getting to know and discover himself. In addition; Listening, talking, introducing yourself, meeting a new person, understanding the other person, expressing your feelings, anger management, sharing, taking responsibility, understanding, in situations such as communication in social life will be created with tips on how to be.To gain mastery of the language rules necessary for literary presentation</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412056&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
