    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Recognize the concept of creativity. Classify the branches of art. Learn the method of drama. Develop creative thinking skills. Use creative techniques. Apply creative and artistic activities in social and professional life. Evaluate the obstacles in front of creativity.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411823&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="45">
