   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 197</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to Art Therapy</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Sanat Terapisine Giriş dersinde teorik materyaller ve deneyimsel aktivitelerle sanat terapisine giriş niteliğinde pratik sağlarken, psikoloji, sanat tarihi, felsefe, antropoloji gibi alanlardan örnekler ele alınacaktır.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412086&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="60">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 198</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Non-Clinical Applications in Art Therapy</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bu ders kapsamında sanat temelli öğrenme yöntemleri, psikososyal destek çalışmalarında sanat ve sanat terapisinin kullanımı, sanat temelli atölye tasarımı konuları ve örnekleri gösterilecektir. Aynı zamanda yaratıcılık üzerine yapılan araştırmalarda ortaya çıkan verilerin incelenmesi ve tartışılması, yaratıcı kişilik özelliğine sahip kişilerin ürettikleri eserlerden yola çıkarak çevreye duyarlılaşma, ileri dönüşüm, yaratıcı problem çözme becerisi elde etme gibi konuların işlendiği içeriğe sahiptir.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412087&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 199</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Women's Studies</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Kadın Çalışmaları dersini başarıyla tamamlayan bir öğrenci öncelikli olarak kadınların yaşamına ilişkin sosyolojik ve feminist perspektiflerin bizi nasıl bilgilendirdiğini görecek, yakın zamanlı olarak ortaya konmuş bazı araştırma ve teorilerini gözden geçirecek.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412088&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 199</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Women's Studies</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Toplumsal cinsiyet kavramı hakkında bilgi sahibi olacak.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412088&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 199</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Women's Studies</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Toplumsal cinsiyet rolleri ile ilgili farkındalığı oluşacak.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412088&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 199</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Women's Studies</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Düşünme ve sorgulama yeteneği gelişecek.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412088&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 199</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Women's Studies</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Sosyal medyanın insanlar üzerindeki etkilerini daha sağlıklı değerlendirebilecek.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412088&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course for Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be able to listen for specific information, main ideas and opinions.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412035&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course for Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be able to read for and understand specific information, main ideas, gist and opinions.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412035&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course for Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be able to write a discursive essay on various topics.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412035&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course for Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be able to write a factual summary.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412035&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course for Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Students will be able to respond to questions on familiar and unfamiliar topics and to speak at length.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412035&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 213</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">English Language Course for Erasmus I</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Academic vocabulary will be targeted; students will be able to use high-level vocabulary.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412035&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 215</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Rights and Health</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Will be able to explain the concept of Human Rights. * Defines the basic concepts related to human rights. * Expresses the importance of Human Rights. * Describe the historical development of Human Rights.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412055&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="45">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 215</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Rights and Health</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">It will be able to specify international and national legal regulations related to human rights and Human Rights Defenders. * Recognizes legal regulations developed at international and national levels for the protection of Human Rights. * Refers to national and international organizations working on Human Rights. * Discusses how protection mechanisms related to human rights work.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412055&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="45">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 215</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Rights and Health</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">It will be able to evaluate the practice of Human Rights in different societies and different groups of society and in different environments. * Discusses human rights practices from the point of view of different groups of society. * Interprets the relationship of human rights with development and social inequality. * Questions Human Rights Practices in emergency situations.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412055&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 215</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Human Rights and Health</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Will be able to interpret the relationship between human rights and health. * Evaluates health as a human right. * Examines the use of the right to health by patients and health workers.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412055&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 217</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">To gain a knowledge of some of the key technological and industrial changes the medium has undergone from 1880-today.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412030&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 217</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">To understand in greater depth several influential aesthetic and stylistic developments of film.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412030&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 217</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">To understand how film is an art form (both narrative and non narrative) and an industrial, theatrical, and non theatrical medium.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412030&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 217</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">To gain an understanding of film as a national, international and global medium.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412030&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 217</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">To critically engage with select examples of academic writing about film history.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412030&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">By the end of the course, the students will have a thorough grasp of the history of the horror film, its formal and narrative strategies, and the various critical and theoretical approaches used to examine it.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412061&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The students will also expand their knowledge of the complex relationship of horror cinema to issues of identity, nation, ideology, and affect.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412061&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Close analysis of major horror films in class and on exams will make the students a more skilled reader and critic of both cinema and the horror genre.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412061&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 223</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Modern Scientific Research Methods</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Scientific research methods, quantitative and qualitative study examples, data analysis through a statistical program, research results, publication and writing techniques, and reporting.</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411824&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 225</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Strategic Brand Management</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Develop an understanding of what brand management is and why it is important</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411943&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 225</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Strategic Brand Management</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Comprehend how to analyze the market and consumer behavior</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411943&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 225</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Strategic Brand Management</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Gain a strong understanding of how marketing and brand strategies ensure sustainable profit</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411943&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 225</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Strategic Brand Management</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Develop a visionary base regarding the harmonization of marketing and brand strategies into implementation</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=411943&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 226</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Project Management</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">To have knowledge about the principles and principles of sector-independent project management at international standards</Data></Cell>
