    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">compare the views of different theorists in the psychoanalytic approach in terms of the nature, functioning of personality and their view of psychopathology.</Data></Cell>
