    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Writing Skill-At the end of this course, students will be able to • comprehend the process of writing from the first stage to the final stage • recognize and produce the style, features and formats typical of academic writing • develop the appropriate range of vocabulary • be familiar with typical contexts and topics</Data></Cell>
