    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">European Art Cinema: French New Wave/ Eastern Europe and Former Soviet Union Films: François Truffaut, France, The 400 Blows (1959). Jean-Luc Godard, France, Breathless (1960). Agnes Varda, France, Cleo from 5 to 7 (1962). MIDTERMS (take-home)</Data></Cell>
