    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Cinema</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">World Cinema Beyond the West: European/ Asian/ Latin American (50’s – 60’s) Films: Akira Kurosawa, Japan, Rashomon (1950). Ingmar Bergman, Sweden, The Seventh Seal (1957). Satyajit Ray, India, Pather Panchali (1955).</Data></Cell>
