   <Row ss:Height="30">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The demonic other (1960’s – 1970’s) Reading: Barbara Creed: “Woman as Possessed Monster: The Exorcist.” in The Monstrous Feminine.31-42. (Available on-line on Google Books) Film: The Exorcist (William Friedkin, 1968), Rosemary’s Baby (Polanski, 1968)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Lecturing</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412061&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
   </Row>
   <Row ss:Height="45">
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Bilgisayar Mühendisliği (İngilizce)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">6246</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 221</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">History of the Horror Film</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">The genre of the slasher and the final girl (1970’s – 1980’s) Reading: Clover, Carol J. “Her Body, Himself: Gender in the Slasher Film.” Horror, the Film Reader. Ed. Mark Jankovich. London: Routledge, 2002. (77-89.) Film: Halloween (Carpenter, 1978), The Texas Chainsaw Massacre (Tobe Hooper, 1974)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Lecturing</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=412061&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
