    <Cell ss:StyleID="s63"><Data ss:Type="String">Seismic (mass) and thermal sensors: Electromechanical resonance, electrochemical forces, Henry’s and ideal gas laws; Surface acoustic wave (SAW) devices; atomic force microscopy; manometric sensors; thermometric detection</Data></Cell>
